{"type":"message","id":"a648cb42","parentId":"d6d51bba","timestamp":"2026-04-14T19:47:54.826Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_lp4hktfv9ddv_2","toolName":"sessions_list","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"count\": 20,\n  \"sessions\": [\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"heartbeat\"\n      },\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 5p Progress Report\",\n      \"displayName\": \"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-cron-ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776196064349,\n      \"sessionId\": \"ec0d6f23-757e-4ed8-8431-3fa69a9287e3\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 20418,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"running\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1776196063839,\n      \"childSessions\": [\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:c2d275a5-d70a-4775-a268-fecf4708f133\",\n        \"agent:planner:subagent:63bb70ce-b5f3-48d0-a236-b6cf5d8d7922\",\n        \"agent:planner:subagent:ba49ac6d-ceff-4a9d-b3b1-7b89afdd88cc\"\n      ],\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/ec0d6f23-757e-4ed8-8431-3fa69a9287e3.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"user\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"[cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7 5p Progress Report — AHV Works] You are the 5-minute change-detecting reporter for the AHV Works ecosystem.\\n\\nCheck sessions_list. Compare current active sessions against the last known state stored in memory/heartbeat-state.json.\\n\\n**If nothing has changed since the last report:**\\n- Stay SILENT. Send nothing. Not even HEARTBEAT_OK. Just exit quietly.\\n\\n**If there IS a change** (new session spawned, session died, agent failed, blocker appeared, task completed), compose a concise change report to group -5163901258:\\n\\nFormat:\\n🟡 Orbis — 5p Update | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\\n\\nChanges detected:\\n• [list of actual changes]\\n\\nPipeline: {HEALTHY if no failures / DEGRADED if failures}\\n• Active sessions: N\\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\\n• Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\\n• Blockers: none / [list blockers]\\n\\nOnly send when something changed. Stay silent when stable.\\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 - 7:46 PM (UTC) / 2026-04-14 19:46 UTC\\n\\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1776196063838,\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"874b3102\",\n            \"seq\": 1\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"This is a cron job asking me to check for changes and report if there are any. Let me:\\n1. Read the current heartbeat-state.json from memory\\n2. Check sessions_list to see current state\\n3. Compare and report if there are changes\\n\\nLet me start by reading the heartbeat state and checking sessions.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_lp4hktfv9ddv_1\",\n              \"name\": \"memory_search\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"query\": \"heartbeat-state.json\",\n                \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n              }\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"c