tch MCP wrapper test, stitch-connect skill update, BE merge decision pending\\n- Blockers: BE is 11 commits behind remote on notification system, Lead decision needed for merge\\n\\nCurrent time is 10:00 PM UTC (10:00 PM Monday April 13), so this briefing covers the day and sets up for Tuesday.\\n\\n\\nNow I'll format this as a status report.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"🌅 **ORBIS MORNING BRIEFING**\\n📅 Monday, April 13, 2026\\n⏰ 10:00 PM UTC | 5:00 AM UTC+7\\n\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n\\n**1️⃣ YESTERDAY'S COMPLETED TASKS**\\n\\n✅ **AHV Works Review** — FULL REVIEW COMPLETE (commit 84cdb2d)\\n✅ **Session Recovery** — Crash at 00:34 UTC (HTTP 500 / context overflow), fully recovered on model `AHV-Holding-DEV`\\n✅ **FE Sync** — Frontend fully synchronized with remote develop ✅\\n✅ **DTLX/QLHV Systems** — Stable, shared DB architecture operational\\n✅ **34-Agent Ecosystem** — SKILL_GATES, HANDOVER/FEEDBACK, OPENSPEC all verified ✅\\n\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n\\n**2️⃣ TODAY'S PRIORITIES**\\n\\n🔴 **P0 — AHV Works Fixes** — 13 unresolved P0 issues queued for resolution\\n🟡 **Stitch MCP Wrapper** — Complete integration testing post-gateway restart\\n🟡 **stitch-connect Skill** — Update to use MCP wrapper (replacing OAuth flow)\\n🔵 **BE Notification System** — Local behind remote by 11 commits; notification system feature pending merge\\n\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n\\n**3️⃣ BLOCKERS & RISKS**\\n\\n⚠️ **BE Merge Conflict** — Backend is 11 commits behind remote on `notification-system`; remote is 2 commits ahead on `data-isolation`. **Lead decision required** before merge can proceed.\\n\\n⚠️ **Context Overflow Risk** — Session crash root cause identified (200k+ tokens / model instability). Monitor session health closely.\\n\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n\\n**Pipeline Status:** 🟢 HEALTHY\\n**Active Agents:** 34 (v4 ecosystem)\\n**Active Session:** telegram:group:-5212380728\\n\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\nOrbis 🌐 — Global Orchestrator\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 328,\n            \"output\": 570,\n            \"totalTokens\": 17958,\n            \"cacheRead\": 14121,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 2939,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776117671474,\n          \"responseId\": \"062c9aa87844c59bbd285766e62b966f\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"faf39631\",\n            \"seq\": 7\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}[... 51798 more characters truncated]"}],"details":{"count":20,"sessions":[{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","origin":{"provider":"heartbeat"},"label":"Cron: 5p Progress Report","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-cron-ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1776196064349,"sessionId":"ec0d6f23-757e-4ed8-8431-3fa69a9287e3","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":20418,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776196063839,"childSessions":["agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:c2d275a5-d70a-4775-a268-fecf4708f133","agent:planner:subagent:63bb70ce-b5f3-48d0-a236-b6cf5d8d7922","agent:planner:subagent:ba49ac6d-ceff-4a9d-b3b1-7b89afdd88cc"],"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/ec0d6f23-757e-4ed8-8431-3fa69a9287e3.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7 5p Progress Report — AHV Works] You are the 5-minute change-detecting reporter for the AHV Works ecosystem.\n\nCheck sessions_list. Compare current active sessions against the last known state stored in memory/heartbeat-state.json.\n\n**If nothing has changed since the last report:**\n- Stay SILENT. Send nothing. Not even HEARTBEAT_OK. Just exit quietly.\n\n**If there IS a change** (new session spawned, session died, agent failed, blocker appeared, task completed), compose a concise change report to group -5163901258:\n\nFormat:\n🟡 Orbis — 5p Update | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\n\nChanges detected:\n• [list of actual changes]\n\nPipeline: {HEALTHY if no failures / DEGRADED if failures}\n• Active sessions: N\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n• Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\n• Blockers: none / [list blockers]\n\nOnly send when something changed. Stay silent when stable.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 - 7:46 PM (UTC) / 2026-04-14 19:46 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1776196063838,"__openclaw":{"id":"874b3102","seq":1}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job asking me to check for changes and report if there are any. Let me:\n1. Read the current heartbeat-state.json from memory\n2. Check sessions_list to see current state\n3. Compare and report if there are changes\n\nLet me start by reading the heartbeat state and checking sessions."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lp4hktfv9ddv_1","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"heartbeat-state.json","corpus":"memory"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lp4hktfv9ddv_2","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"limit":20,"messageLimit":3}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":438,"output":136,"totalTokens":14518,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776196064028,"responseId":"062dcce1fc92143aeb64738c7153cb52","__openclaw":{"id